<div class="container">
  <div class="jumbotron">
  <p> Welcome to Melody !! This is a database, where logged in User can assign, music instrument and track enrollments with Create, Read, Update and Delete capability.</p>
  <p> User can see the list of all instruments and all enrollments created by other users but can edit and delete only their records.</p>
  <h5> Follow the below guidance to assign the instrument correctly<h4>
  <h6>:: :: As a user you can choose three Levels - Beginner, Intermediate and Experienced</h6>
  <h6>:: :: Ensure to choose the Price and Minimum duration based on the Levels</h6>
  <li>Beginner -> $39 per session -> 16 weeks</li>
  <li>Intermediate -> $49 per session -> 8 weeks</li>
  <li>Experienced -> $89 per session -> 4 weeks</li>
  </div>
  </div>
  <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover">
    <thead class="thead-light">
      <tr>
        <th>Instrument</th>
        <th>Enrolled Student</th>
        <th>Session Start Date</th>
        <th>Level</th>
        <th>Session Price</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <% @user.enrollments.each do |enrollment| %>
         <tr>
            <td><%= enrollment.instrument.name %></td>
            <td><%= enrollment.student %></td>
            <td><%= enrollment.startdate.strftime("%b %d,%Y") %></td>
            <td><%= enrollment.level %></td>
            <td><%= number_to_currency(enrollment.price) %></td>
          <%  if enrollment.user.id == current_user.id %> 
          <td><%= link_to "Edit Enrollment", edit_enrollment_path(enrollment.id), method: :edit %>
          <td><%= button_to "Delete Enrollment", enrollment_path(enrollment.id), method: :delete, data: { confirm: "Are you sure you want to delete the lesson?"}, class: "btn btn-xs btn-danger" %>
          <% end %> 
          </tr>
  <% end %>  
</div>
  
    